node.text:
I teamed up with @turtlebeach to create an exclusive custom version of one of my favorite gaming headsets, the Stealth 700 Gen 2. Even better, now you have a chance to win one of these limited edition headsets! UPDATE: Winners have been announced in the link in bio! 

- Follow @turtlebeach

- Tag 2 friends
- Enter using the link in my bio! 

Good luck! #HearEverything
